      <h2 class="border-b">What we believe about Parenting</h2>
      <p>Preschool Farm Fun was created in conjunction with Humanswithkids.com. One of the foundational beliefs of Humans With Kids is that Parents should seek to become a legend in their homes. The truth is, you will never have more influence on anyone more than you do with your children. We are constantly creating and curating ways to help you cultivate that influence. Great health is something any parent desires for their children. While we can’t change our genes, we can influence our habits. So, we created Preschool Farm Fun. We want to make veggies fun. So use it that way. Play with your kids, then take them with you to the grocery store with you. Instead of dreading the candy aisle, start looking forward to the produce aisle. Ask your kids to pick out their favorite veggies. Count them, name them, and then use them to create a foundation for eating right.</p>
    </div>
